data.name: ChkFileDescLabel.Text
data.value:
Download and extract your Snapchat data from
Then, inside the extracted folder, go into the “json” folder and locate the file “memories_history.json” and copy it to the same location as this program. Once done, click the button below to ensure the application can see it. Once it finds your file, PLEASE DO NOT REMOVE THIS FILE FROM THIS LOCATION until the program is done running and all your files are downloaded.

data.name: DownloadDescLabel.Text
data.value: Now the application can begin downloading your memories into a folder called “Snap Memories” in the same location as this program. This may take quite a while, so please DO NOT close the program while it is running.
